<p align="justify"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;"><span><b><span>Gastos no devengados</span></b></span></span></span></p>
<p align="justify"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;"><span><b><span>480 GASTOS ANTICIPADOS.</span></b></span></span></span></p>
<p align="justify"><span color="#202020" style="color: #202020;"><span face="Verdana, serif" style="font-family: Verdana, serif;"><span><b><span>567 INTERESES PAGADOS POR ANTICIPADO (si el gasto tiene carácter financiero).</span></b></span></span></span></p>
